package testchain

// erc721BytecodeHex is the creation bytecode for the minimal test ERC-721
// (TestNFT721): ERC-165 supportsInterface (0x01ffc9a7 + 0x80ac58cd), ownerOf,
// a public mint(to,id), and the canonical safeTransferFrom(from,to,id)
// (0x42842e0e). It deliberately omits approvals/operators/name()/symbol() and the
// receiver-callback — the smallest contract that passes ERC-165 721 detection and
// moves ownership for a real on-chain assertion. Compiled offline with solc 0.8.26
// (optimizer on) from src/TestNFT721.sol and checked in so the integration test
// needs no solc at run time. See erc721.go for the deploy + raw-RPC readers.
const erc721BytecodeHex = ""
